  m_Name: NightOfTheLivingBunniesWarriorDialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  resourceName: Night Of The Living Bunnies (Warrior)
  icon: {fileID: 0}
  description: 
  resourceDescriptionProfile: 
  automatic: 0
  repeatable: 0
  audioProfileName: 
  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It looks like you will get to hunt bunnies after all.  '
    nextOption: Really?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: "The bunnies killed by the zombies have come back to life.  \n\nThis
      presents an opportunity to practice using your new abilities.  \n\nKill 5 reanimated
      bunnies.  Be sure to use Shield Flash, Threatening Strike, Hard Kick, and Warming
      Ray at least once."
    nextOption: But I don't have any weapons...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Once you have defeated the bunnies, it should be safe to collect
      the ingredients for your weapons.


      We also have an opportunity to do something about your clothing situation.'
    nextOption: Great, I'm starting to get cold
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: "You can make a suit of armor for yourself using nearby ingredients.
      \ \n\nYou can get started with the leather for the boots."
    nextOption: But I don't know how to make...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It''s easy!


      Just collect the skins from the bunnies when you take care of them.'
    nextOption: I have to use dead bunny skins?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Go deal with the bunnies.


      When you have your weapons and armor, return to me for your next assignment.'
    nextOption: But I don't know how to make...
  prerequisiteConditions: []
